# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository (consistent across Windows,
# macOS, Linux, and CI). Prevents CRLF/LF churn and keeps Prettier happy.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never normalize or diff.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary

# Lockfile: treat as text but don't show diffs (it's machine-generated).
pnpm-lock.yaml -diff
